'''Aṭṭan affalman''' d tagrawt [[aṭṭan|waṭṭanen]] i d-yettilin s usrag webrir (s ssebba n feccal) d tamumt n [[Anagraw anaffal|unagraw anaffal]] n [[tafekka|tfekka]] n [[Amuddir|umuddir]] deg tussna d tukza ɣef [[agman|yigmanen-is]] d imuren-is igensasen. Anda ur izemmer ara ad yakez tukkest n ADN n [[tabniqt|tekwatin]] n tfekka sin akin ad yessalas (ad yemɛamal) yid-sent amakken-itent d ajenṭad neɣ d uffiɣ ayen yettaǧǧan ad yenṭeg fell-asent  s tekwatin tfekkiwin n [[affal|waffal]] 

Dɣa anecta i gellu-d s tiɣessirin (ixeṣṣaren) meqqren g tfekka, tiɣessirin-a zemrent  ad ilint deg yiwen n [[agman|ugman]] am [[taɣbelt]] neɣ deg yigmanen yemgaraden i wakken ad yeglu s waṭṭan neɣ s waṭas n waṭṭanen 

Tella tdersi meqqren n yimdanen deg umadal ilan (yesɛan) aṭṭanen-a yettilin d [[aṭṭan yezgan|imezrayen]] deg tuget n tegnatin, 

== Isemda == 
Istigen sskanayen-d d akken aṭṭanen iffalmanen gan gar 10 n waṭṭanen imezwura deg yisragen n [[timekkest|tmekkasin]] (lmut) ɣer [[tawtemt|tmeṭṭuyin]] seg waddaren yakk alamma d 65 n iseggasen.<ref>{{cite journal|aneggar1=Walsh|amezwar1=SJ|aneggar2=Rau|amezwar2=LM|azwel=Autoimmune diseases: a leading cause of death among young and middle-aged women in the United States.|journal=American journal of public health|azmez=September 2000|volume=90|issue=9|tasniwin=1463–6|pmid=10983209|pmc=1447637|doi=10.2105/ajph.90.9.1463}}</ref> Tella tdersi n yimdanen ilan uguren-a n waṭṭanen igan d imezrayen deg tuget n tegnatin, akken illan ugar n 80 n waṭṭanen asrag-nsen d aṭṭan affalman.<ref>{{Amnir n web | akala=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/000816.htm | azwel=MedlinePlus medical encyclopedia - autoimmune disorders | azmez=16 July 2014 | anefsar=National Institutes of Health | azmez n tuwwṭa=21 December 2014| akala n ufaylu = https://web.archive.org/web/20160705041038/https://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/000816.htm | azmez n ufaylu = 05 yulyu 2016 }}</ref>

